title: Justin Bieber's dad is proud of his son's cock
text:
Justin Bieber's nude pictures from his Bora Bora vacation have finally caught his "proud" daddy's eye.

The 21-year- old singer's father, Jeremy Bieber, took to twitter to express his happiness about his son's stuff, saying "What do you feed that thing? #proud daddy," TMZ reported. However, the ' Baby' hit-maker's legal team is now sending out notices to get the controversial pictures down.

Source have revealed that Bieber has claimed that his privacy was invaded by this act and has asked every media outlet, who published his pictures that was shot in Bora Bora, to take them down immediately.
